DocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526118\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bmd1665702876394.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bmd1665702876394.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bmd1665702876394.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bmd1665702876394\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Create\n      an installation user profile </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To install Uniface,  you must use a user profile that has restore authority on the iSeries\n      system. </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__context_w2701ab1b5b1_w2702ab1b5_w2703ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66053e1_d66054e1_d66055e1\">The iSeries restore commands <code class=\"ph codeph\">RSTLIB</code>\n            and <code class=\"ph codeph\">RSTOBJ</code> are usually shipped with a public authority level of\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">*EXCLUDE</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66068e1_d66069e1_d66070e1\">We recommend that you use user profile UNIFSID to\n            install Uniface , and that you give UNIFSID an authority level equivalent to that for QSECOFR for\n            installing Uniface. Consult your iSeries system administrator if this is not possible. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66071e1_d66072e1_d66073e1\">After installation you can reduce the authority level\n            of UNIFSID, although it still requires <code class=\"ph codeph\">*ALLOBJ</code> and\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">*JOBCTL</code> if it will be used to run the Uniface Router job.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__note_gms_zfx_wvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> In this documentation, UNIFSID is assumed to be the\n            user profile in use.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66074e1_d66075e1_d66076e1\">If you use a different profile than UNIFSID, or you do\n            not give UNIFSID the level of authority equivalent to QSECOFR, then the following\n            considerations apply:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__ul_c4z_zfx_wvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__li_d28811e1_d28812e1_d28813e1\">User profile UNIFSID is the owner of the objects\n               in the installation savefile. If this profile does not exist, the owner becomes\n               QDFTOWN. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__li_d28814e1_d28815e1_d28816e1\">The operating system does not allow\n               system-provided user profiles (such as QSECOFR and QSYSOPR) to be the owner of\n               Uniface Router job. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__li_d28817e1_d28818e1_d28819e1\">The user using <span class=\"ph filepath\">AS400INS</span> or\n               running <code class=\"ph codeph\">LODRUN</code> must have <code class=\"ph codeph\">*USE</code> authority for the\n               following CL commands: <code class=\"ph codeph\">CRTJOBD</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">CRTJOBQ</code>,\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">CRTSBSD</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">CRTCLS</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">CRTPRTF</code>,\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">RSTLIB</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">RSTOBJ</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">CPY</code>, and\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">CPYFRMSTMF</code>. <p class=\"p\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66077e1_d66078e1_d66079e1\">Alternatively,\n                  the user must have <code class=\"ph codeph\">*ALLOBJ</code> authority and, if\n                     <span class=\"ph filepath\">AS400INS</span> is used to create a subsystem,\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">*JOBCTL</code> authority.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__li_d28820e1_d28821e1_d28822e1\">The user using <span class=\"ph filepath\">AS400INS</span> or\n               running <code class=\"ph codeph\">LODRUN</code> must be authorized to create a directory in the IFS,\n               under <code class=\"ph codeph\">/</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">/QopenSys</code>. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66080e1_d66081e1_d66082e1\">To create a user profile for the owner of the Uniface product objects:</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__li_d28823e1_d28824e1_d28825e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66083e1_d66084e1_d66085e1\">Use the following command:\n where <var class=\"keyword varname\">Password</var>is the password associated with the UNIFSID user profile.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">CRTUSRPRF UNIFSID PASSWORD(<var class=\"keyword varname\">Password</var>)\n USRCLS(*PGMR) SPCAUT(*ALLOBJ *JOBCTL)\n TEXT('Uniface Product User Profile')\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__note_w2704ab1b5b3b1b3b3_w2705ab1b5b3b1b3_w2706ab1b5b3b1_w2707ab1b5b3_w2708ab1b5_w2709ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> UNIFSID was the owner of the Uniface objects when the objects were saved. To properly reestablish Uniface object ownership, the UNIFSID ID should exist before the Uniface product is installed.</div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__li_d28826e1_d28827e1_d28828e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__p_d66086e1_d66087e1_d66088e1\">If you are using a different code page from the default Uniface code page, you must add the additional parameter <code class=\"ph codeph\">CCSID(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CodePage</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>where <var class=\"keyword varname\">CodePage</var>is one of the supported Uniface code pages:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__table_d5798e1_d5799e1_d5800e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"bmd1665702876394__table_d5798e1_d5799e1_d5800e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"bmd1665702876394__table_d5798e1_d5799e1_d5800e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Code page-0-0\" id=\"topic-Code page-0-0\" name=\"topic-Code page-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Code page-0-0\">Code page</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-CCSID-1-0\" id=\"topic-CCSID-1-0\" name=\"topic-CCSID-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-CCSID-1-0\">CCSID</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label><input aria-label=\"Filter results in the table\" class=\"zDocsInputField\" id=\"search-all-smart-table\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><button aria-label=\"Submit\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldSearch\" type=\"submit\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-search\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-search\"></use></svg></button><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">19 rows found</div></div>